			<p><strong>Monday, April 20, 2026, 2:00–6:00 pm (14:00–18:00 CEST)</strong></p>
			<p>
				<strong>Venue:</strong> Palazzo della Gran Guardia, <strong>Room:</strong> Bohème — Verona, Italy
